  "prompt": "Where can I see a Lamborghini in Bangalore?",
  "response": "If you're in Bangalore and want to see a Lamborghini, here are a few places where you might have a chance:\n\n1. **Lamborghini Bangalore Showroom**:  \n   - The official Lamborghini dealership in Bangalore is located at **No. 303, 60 Feet Road, Koramangala Industrial Layout, 6th Block, Koramangala**.  \n   - This is the best place to see the latest models and possibly even test drive one.  \n\n2. **Luxury Car Events**:  \n   - Keep an eye out for luxury car exhibitions or supercar meetups in Bangalore. Events like the **Bangalore Auto Expo** or **Supercar Sunday** often feature Lamborghinis.  \n\n3. **High-End Hotels and Malls**:  \n   - Luxury hotels like **The Leela Palace** or **Taj West End**, or upscale malls like **Phoenix Marketcity**, sometimes have supercars parked outside or showcased during events.  \n\n4. **Racetracks**:  \n   - Lamborghinis are occasionally seen at tracks like the **MMRT (Madras Motor Race Track)** near Chennai or private events at the **Kari Motor Speedway** in Coimbatore, though these are not in Bangalore.  \n\n5. **Social Media Groups**:  \n   - Join Bangalore-based car enthusiast groups on platforms like Facebook or Instagram. Members often share sightings and meetups for luxury cars.  \n\nIf you're visiting the showroom, it's a good idea to call ahead and confirm their hours and availability of specific models. Enjoy your Lamborghini experience! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
